      <description>Photoshopベータ版に2D画像を回転させる「Rotate Object」機能が追加された。Harmonizeで光と影を調整し、シーンに馴染ませる。</description>
      <content:encoded>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kris Kashtanova&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;a href="https://x.com/icreatelife"&gt;@icreatelife&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; We just released Rotate Object in Photoshop (beta) &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;You can now rotate 2D images!  &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Then use Harmonize to add light and shadows, to blend it perfectly with the rest of the scene. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;It's like Turntable in Illustrator, but instead of vectors, it's pixels in Photoshop!&lt;/p&gt;
